title: FEC, Attribute join between Bush-Cheney and Obama donors in New York city, New York City, 2004, 2008
name: FEC, Attribute join between Bush-Cheney and Obama donors in New York city, New York City, 2004, 2008
description:
The point shape file shows the results of attribute join between Bush-Cheney donors from 2004 and Obama donors in 2008 (Jan to Apr 2008).The attribute used for "join" operation is concatenated x and y coordinates of geocoded donor records of both campaigns. Note that only those records with geocoding score of 90 plus and with the geocoding attribute of "Street Address" or "Address Points" were used. Since there can be more than one record per donor, multiple records were aggregated to single record and donations added together for such multiple record. All those with geocoding score of less than 90 and geocoding attribute of "Zipcode" or "City-State" centroid were dropped.
